OL,5, PepsiCo has been sued by New York state
OL,6, for plastic pollution along Buffalo    
OL,7, River that is allegedly contaminating  
OL,8, the water and harming wildlife.        
OL,10,FAccording to the lawsuit, PepsiCo is   
OL,11,Fthe single largest identifiable        
OL,12,Fcontributor to the problem.            
OL,14,FPepsiCo's spokesperson has told the BBC
OL,15,Fthat it has been "transparent in its   
OL,16,Fjourney to reduce use of plastic".     
OL,18,FLast week Coca-Cola, Danone and Nestle 
OL,19,Fwere accused of making misleading      
OL,20,Fclaims about their plastic bottles.    
